Class Service

java.lang.Object
com.gersonfaneto.yams.models.services.Service
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Service extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the Services that can be requested by the Clients of the Assistance and performed by its Technicians, after being grouped in a Work Order.
